		    <title id="i2127573" xtrf="GSAR" class="- topic/title " xtrc="GSAR">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">517.208</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d336e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
					          <p id="d333e17" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             For solicitations under Federal Acquisition Service’s Special Order Program, insert a provision substantially the same as the provision at <xref href="GSAM-i1876782.dita#i1876782"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">552.217-70</xref>, Evaluation of Options, if both of the following conditions apply:</p>
					          <ol id="d336e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
							              <p id="d333e30" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The solicitation contains an option to extend the term of the contract.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
							              <p id="d333e39" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The contract will be fixed price and contain an economic price adjustment clause.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
					          <p id="d333e50" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             Insert the provision at <xref href="GSAM-i1876791.dita#i1876791"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">552.217-71</xref>, Notice Regarding Option(s), or a similar provision, in solicitations that include an option for increased quantities of supplies or services or an option to extend.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
			      <p class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR"/>
